<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-40-1156 </DOCNO><TEXT>The first chapter, 'Solar energy - more than just Utopia' deals with thefollowing: Alternatives to nuclear energy problems of energy supply,solar energy use, commencement of the solar age in space, solar technologyin the Federal Republic of Germany, solar collectors, wind power, energyfrom hydrogen. The second chapter 'Solar energy - its contribution tofuture energy supply' discusses prospects for the future (interviewswith scientists and engineers). The third and last chapter gives practicalhints (solar energy use: self-construction of solar plants). (HWJ).</TEXT></DOC>